divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking and taking photos of the landscape. I've decide to take some photos of the sky as well. I didn't see anything at the time but then I checked the photo there was something that looked like a cigar. I thought it was a UFO. It was white, long and a shape of a cigar. I was amazed. I losed a sight of the object as I walked further.
